        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Yet in its tone, wellness Instagram still retains some of its original scepticism of the medical establishment. And while some influencers may believe they are genuine truth tellers, the platform's architecture rewards more extreme and emotive content with followers and engagement.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
